:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"推去twitter"},{"pid":"6b7be3beda467419d56a66bab003302098131828","tid":1613932,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"張圖仲有個核彈<br />\n話武力指引只供參考<br />\n警員可以自行判斷合適武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194b9595589f0b24f5baf4601bbf93d664a02161","tid":1613932,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b7be3beda467419d56a66bab003302098131828","tid":1613932,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"張圖仲有個核彈<br />\n話武力指引只供參考<br />\n警員可以自行判斷合適武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"之前有條612 嘅片講左<br />\n班狗自爆做乜都係自己，未必要聽指揮官"},{"pid":"d450fd76bf13ce963c5f31e7e102953698f48d9a","tid":1613932,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"是撚旦啦，中國蝗軍依家大撚晒架啦！"}]}